	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;Serving Food in Itapororoca&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;One of the most touching memories was when we distributed food to people in need, an act that made us realize the critical reality in which many communities lived.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We also visited the communities of &lt;strong&gt;Olinda&lt;/strong&gt; and &lt;strong&gt;Alto do Mateus&lt;/strong&gt;, where we saw up close the precarious living conditions of the local people.&lt;/p&gt;
