&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Without a doubt, my favorite project was &lt;strong&gt;Beira da Linha&lt;/strong&gt;. Here we assisted teachers in their lessons and I had the opportunity to interact with children and young people who attended after-school activities.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/04_experiences/brazil/beihra.jpeg&#34;
	width=&#34;4032&#34;
