		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;These young people, coming from difficult backgrounds, aspired to a better future, and my bond with them was extraordinary. The possibility of contributing to their educational journey was one of the most rewarding experiences of my life.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;http://localhost:1313/04_experiences/brazil/organizers.jpeg&#34;
	width=&#34;5712&#34;
