		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;133&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;320px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;And my greatest respect goes to these educators who dedicate their lives to improving that of the new generations&lt;/p&gt;
