&lt;p&gt;During our stay there, as a tradition in Brazil, we played football a lot&amp;hellip;but the difference was that we were all playing barefoot on the concrete since they only had one pair of shoes, or sometimes not even those and therefore they couldn&amp;rsquo;t/didn&amp;rsquo;t want to ruin them&lt;/p&gt;
