&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Back home, I can finally reflect on what I experienced and assimilate the messages and lessons learned.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Three months have passed since I returned, but the emotions and experiences I lived in Brazil continue to influence my daily life.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We shared so much in only three weeks and when it comes to my mind it seems like a film&amp;hellip;too good to be true&lt;/p&gt;
